nl.tno.stormcv.model.serializer

Class CVParticleSerializer<Type extends CVParticle>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.esotericsoftware.kryo.Serializer<Type>
      • nl.tno.stormcv.model.serializer.CVParticleSerializer<Type>
  • Type Parameters:
    Type - extends GenericType and indicates the objects this serializer will be able to (de)serialize
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DescriptorSerializer, FeatureSerializer, FrameSerializer, GroupOfFramesSerializer, VideoChunkSerializer

    public abstract class CVParticleSerializer<Type extends CVParticle>
extends com.esotericsoftware.kryo.Serializer<Type>
    Abstract class used to serialize subclasses of CVParticle implementations. This class contains the basic methods which can be called by others to (de)serialize objects. Subclasses must be registered to Storm configuration in order for Storm to use them.
    Author:
    Corne Versloot
